 Installation & Setup
1. Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/vaishnavibhosle8010-rgb/SheildAI.git
2. Move into project folder
cd "exora project"
3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run the application
python app.py
